Description: Deepin Water - 桌面喝水提醒助手
 A fun and non-intrusive desktop water drinking reminder with
 immersive fullscreen animations.
 Features 7 animation themes (ocean wave, galaxy spiral, aurora flow,
 thunder storm, fire inferno, bamboo rain, cherry blossom),
 system tray integration, customizable reminder intervals,
 drinking history tracking, daily goals, fun quotes, and sound effects.
